				Posted in <a href="https://venmurasu.in/category/%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%a9%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%a9%e0%ae%bf%e0%ae%b0%e0%af%81-%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%9f%e0%af%88%e0%ae%95%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%95%e0%ae%b3%e0%ae%ae%e0%af%8d/" rel="category tag">பன்னிரு படைக்களம்</a> <span class="on-date"> on <a href="https://venmurasu.in/2016/06/03/%e0%ae%a8%e0%af%82%e0%ae%b2%e0%af%8d-%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%a4%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%a4%e0%af%81-%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%a9%e0%af%8d%e0%ae%a9%e0%ae%bf%e0%ae%b0%e0%af%81-%e0%ae%aa%e0%ae%9f%e0%af%88%e0%ae%95%e0%af%8d-69/" rel="bookmark" title="12:00 முப"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-06-03T00:00:29+05:30">ஜூன் 3, 2016</time></a></span><span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://venmurasu.in/author/mahasrinivasan/" rel="author" title="SS எழுதிய எல்லா இடுகைகளையும் பார்க்கவும்">SS</a></span></span>.
				
